Tyrael: Please do so, Shadow Star, but do not go too fast. I have to 
send a report to the Council.

He opens a channel to the Tripredacus headquarters.

Tyrael: Tripredacus High Council, Major Tyrael reporting. I have 
gathered a crew consisting of Myself, Lieutenant Shadow Star, and 
soldiers Naga and Talon. We will follow the Predacon ship led by 
Megatron. I am bringing the protoforms you gave me, as well as a 
reformatting-capable CR. I will report again as soon as possible and 
if I am still able to do so. Either Megatron will die, or we will kill 
ourselves along with him. Tyrael out. (he closes the channel) 
Strikers, we head out now!
